Handle a Rubik's cube with a terminal UI

# Requirements

* Check test framework
* NCurses
* Conan package maanager

# Install

* git clone https://github.com/libcheck/check.git
* mkdir build-Release-check
* mkdir install-Release-check
* cd build-Release-check
* cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=../install-Release-check ../check
* make install
* cd ..
* git clone https://github.com/mikkoi/rubik.git
* mkdir build-Release-rubik
* cd build-Release-rubik
* pyenv local $(pyenv whence conan)
* conan install ../rubik
* cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug -Dcheck_ROOT=../install-Release-check ../rubik
* make

